theorem Topology.dense_implies_dense_interior_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} :
    Dense (A : Set X) → Dense (interior (closure (A : Set X))) := by
  intro hDense
  dsimp [Dense] at *
  have h :=
    Topology.dense_implies_closure_interior_closure_eq_univ (X := X) (A := A) hDense
  simpa using h

theorem Topology.closure_inter_interior_closure_eq_interior_closure {X : Type*}
    [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    (closure (A : Set X)) ∩ interior (closure A) = interior (closure A) := by
  ext x
  constructor
  · intro hx
    exact hx.2
  · intro hx
    exact And.intro (interior_subset hx) hx
